                    <p>Expert diagnosis and treatment for disorders of the nervous system, brain, and spinal cord.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-baby"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Pediatrics</h3>
                    <p>Specialized medical care for infants, children, and adolescents in a child-friendly environment.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-bone"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Orthopedics</h3>
                    <p>Treatment for musculoskeletal injuries and conditions, from sports injuries to joint replacement.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Ophthalmology</h3>
                    <p>Complete eye care services including vision correction, cataract surgery, and retinal treatments.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-teeth"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Dental Care</h3>
                    <p>Comprehensive dental services for all ages, from routine cleanings to advanced restorative procedures.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="section features">
        <div class="container" id="whyChooseUs">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2 >
                    Why Choose CareDev</h2>
                <p>We are committed to providing exceptional healthcare with a focus on patient-centered care and medical excellence.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-md"></i>
                    <h3>Expert Doctors</h3>
                    <p>Our team includes board-certified physicians with extensive experience in their specialties.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-clinic-medical"></i>
                    <h3>Advanced Technology</h3>
                    <p>We utilize the latest medical technology for accurate diagnosis and effective treatments.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-ambulance"></i>
                    <h3>Emergency Care</h3>
                    <p>24/7 emergency services with rapid response times and specialized trauma care.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i>
                    <h3>Patient-Centered</h3>
                    <p>We prioritize your comfort and well-being with personalized care plans and support.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Need Immediate Medical Assistance?</h2>
            <p>Our emergency department is open 24/7 with specialized medical staff ready to provide immediate care.</p>
            <button class="btn btn-light rounded-pill">Emergency Contact +27 55 084 </button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-grid">
                <div class="footer-col">
                    <h3>CareDev Hospital</h3>
                    <p>Providing exceptional healthcare services with compassion and cutting-edge technology since 1995.</p>
                    <div class="social-links">
                        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-col">
                    <h3>Quick Links</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a asp-controller="Home">Home</a></li>
                        <li><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="AboutUs">About Us</a></li>
                        <li><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Privacy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
                        <li><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Developers">Developers</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-col">
                    <h3><a href="#services">Services</a></h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Cardiology</li>
